Title : Magnetic resonance imaging of pediatric atraumatic musculoskeletal lesions.
Date : 1990
Publication_type : Journal Article
Abstract : MRI has become a useful study for evaluating the musculoskeletal system. This article discusses the technique of pediatric musculoskeletal MRI and its practical applications. MRI appearances of various pathologic entities, including infection, neoplasms, marrow disorders, and joint diseases, are also reviewed.
